cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new deep reinforcement learning agent that is able to rapidly assimilate new experiences and act upon them. The paper focuses on the efficiency of the agent and its ability to learn significantly faster than other state-of-the-art, general purpose deep reinforcement learning agents. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
